videos.description: Vitto Brown gets the pass from D'Mitrik Trice and puts down a big slam.

D. Mostella makes the tough shot and gets fouled

videos.description: Tennessee tightens up on defense and swats Wisconsin's shot, leading to Lamonte Turner's layup on the other end.
videos.headline: Tennessee turns defense into offense

videos.description: Admiral Schofield gets the big block in transition to deny Wisconsin.

videos.description: Tennessee's Shembari Phillips makes a tough runner and gets fouled to cut into the Badgers' lead.
videos.headline: Phillips makes tough runner to cut into Wisconsin's lead

videos.description: Nigel Hayes knocks down a clutch 3-pointer to extend Wisconsin's lead to nine points.
